{"tid":1395790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回歸吉祥物中華白海豚僅剩32條","createTime":"2019-08-02T00:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T04:14:47.000Z","uid":4942,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"481d7abc91be5a0afcfe1c0a078ec9aecefc16da","tid":1395790,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:59:06.000Z","msg":"【當我們只剩下32個白海豚手足🐬😢】<br />\n<br />\n🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬<br />\n🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬<br />\n🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬🐬<br />\n(無錯，呢度就係所有香港嘅白海豚了😢)<br />\n<br />\n漁護署今日公佈最新的海豚數字，去年香港水域只剩下32條白海豚，繼前年47條後，再度刷歷史新低！(數字指平均每日有32條海豚使用香港水域)不單止數量最低，海豚無以往咁大群 、海豚新力軍越來越少、海豚連同朋友社交遊玩的時間都少咗添，揾食艱難呀！<br />\n<br />\n起完港珠澳大橋又點？第三跑大白象起得如火如荼😔<br />\n白海豚邊有時間同空間可以抖氣？<br />\n<br />\n雖然政府準備係大嶼山南面、西南面劃兩個保護區，但係南面的高速船不但將保護區分開，仲令到白海豚更危險，然而政府和海事處仲未正視高速船改道對保護白海豚的重要性！請大家幫幫手，一齊聯署，一齊將白海豚手足的苦況話俾更多人知 🙏<br />\n<br />\n#32條白海豚手足 #出年又會淨返幾多呢<br />\n#收復豚地 #航道南移 #連接兩個保護區<br />\n#白海豚堅持住呀 #香港人堅持住呀<br />\n▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️<br />\n【延伸】<br />\n✏聯署「收復豚地」救救白海豚<br />\n&rarr; <a href=\"http://bit.ly/savehkdolphin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fsavehkdolphin&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=6f514d37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/savehkdolphin</a><br />\n🎥 4/8《白海豚失樂園》紀錄片放映<br />\n&rarr; <a href=\"http://bit.ly/cotsdcsform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fcotsdcsform&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=a1241089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/cotsdcsform</a> (名額有限)<br />\n🔎 招人全職項目主任<br />\n &rarr; <a href=\"http://hk.hkdcs.org/get-involved/job-opportunity/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.hkdcs.org%2Fget-involved%2Fjob-opportunity%2F&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=f4931b2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.hkdcs.org/get-involved/job-opportunity/</a><br />\n📖 閱讀漁護署最新中華白海豚報告<br />\n&rarr;<a href=\"https://www.afcd.gov.hk/english//conservation/con_mar/con_mar_chi/con_mar_chi_chi/files/Final_Report_2018_19.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afcd.gov.hk%2Fenglish%2F%2Fconservation%2Fcon_mar%2Fcon_mar_chi%2Fcon_mar_chi_chi%2Ffiles%2FFinal_Report_2018_19.pdf&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=301d089d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.afcd.gov.hk/english//conservation/con_mar/con_mar_chi/con_mar_chi_chi/files/Final_Report_2018_19.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfrom hkcds fb :<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107811049386054/posts/1331759116991235?s=690569038&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107811049386054%2Fposts%2F1331759116991235%3Fs%3D690569038%26sfns%3Dmo&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=ee735677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107811049386054/posts/1331759116991235?s=690569038&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"1558737eec8b74dc0d53f06b477cefeb582419ca","tid":1395790,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:00:00.000Z","msg":"救救海豚🐬"},{"pid":"515f8ad99be4353b2b524b1a30f6fa11f1935632","tid":1395790,"uid":4942,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:01:46.000Z","msg":"三跑<br />\n<br />\n仲有明日大嶼<br />\n<br />\n班海豚好快就死撚哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5afbde495e0000c03e153f6435bf4c5619306e0","tid":1395790,"uid":33174,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:09:48.000Z","msg":"當D日官好撚搞笑話D基建起完佢地就會番黎香港"},{"pid":"aeadb8a7cdc22bf0e1b4d1afd833ca2dbbd93c03","tid":1395790,"uid":70505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5afbde495e0000c03e153f6435bf4c5619306e0","tid":1395790,"uid":33174,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:09:48.000Z","msg":"當D日官好撚搞笑話D基建起完佢地就會番黎香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:12:53.000Z